# @haku Engine & Runtime

Docs: `docs/architecture.md` · API: `docs/links.md` · Render roadmap: `RENDER_PLAN.md`

## Boundaries

- **No** `react`, `react-dom`, `@haku/editor` in engine or playground
- **No** `three` in `@haku/core` or `@haku/schema`
- Shipped games use `@haku/engine/runtime` entry only

## Render model

Simulation (`IWorld` components) ≠ Presentation (`RenderSyncSystem` → Three.js).

Key files: `engine.ts`, `render-sync/render-sync-system.ts`, `mesh-factory.ts`, `model-loader.ts`

## Async glTF

Respect `modelLoadId` — ignore stale loader callbacks (`docs/edge-cases.md`).

## Render features

Use `RenderSettings.features.*` — off by default; test flag-off path. Incremental phases in `RENDER_PLAN.md`.

## Verify

```bash
pnpm --filter @haku/engine test
pnpm --filter @haku/playground dev
./scripts/check.sh   # bundle must not contain react-dom / editor strings
```
